# Keep the build context small and reproducible. Anything not needed
# for `dotnet restore`/`publish` or `npm ci`/`build` is excluded.

# .NET artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
**/*.user

# Tests (not needed inside the runtime image)
tests/

# Node
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.vite/
**/.cache/

# VCS / IDE / local tooling
.git/
.github/
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
.claude/

# OS / editor noise
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.swp

# Docs and ops files don't belong in the image
README.md
docker-compose.yml
**/Dockerfile
